text: Gymnothorax mccoskeri is a moray eel found in the western Pacific and the eastern Indian ocean.Gymnothorax mccoskeri at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Smith and Böhlke in 1997, and is commonly known as the McCosker's moray, many-banded moray-eel, or the manyband moray.Common names for Gymnothorax mccoskeri at www.fishbase.org. ==References== mccoskeri Category:Fish described in 1997
